data.description: PRICE DROP!!  Welcome Home!  This stunning split foyer home is nestled in the peaceful Chesapeake Ranch Estates neighborhood. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and airy living space full of natural light from the windows. The main level boasts a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying cozy family nights. The adjoining dining area seamlessly flows into the kitchen complete with modern appliances. The upper level is complete with a primary bedroom with private bathroom,  two additional bedrooms  perfect for family or guests, and a shared full bathroom ensures convenience for all.   The lower level of this home offers endless possibilities, with a generously-sized family room that can easily be transformed into a home theater or game room. A full bathroom and laundry room complete this level, adding to the functionality if this home. The lower level features french doors that lead to the backyard where you'll find a perfect retreat to enjoy the outdoors. The patio provides the perfect spot for outdoor dining and entertaining.  This home has an attached garage with ample parking in front of the home.  This neighborhood features a private lake and two private beaches along with a host of other things. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home - come check it out!!!  This home also has a new driveway, a new HVAC air sanitizer connected to HVAC, new hot water heater, and new retaining wall along the driveway near garage.
